{
  "name": "@jects/elements",
  "version": "0.8.0",
  "description": "Jects UI Web Components — light-DOM custom elements over the framework-agnostic @jects/* engines. One generic factory, per-component typed element classes (config in, engine events out as CustomEvents, .instance for imperative access).",
